ABOUT ME

Who I am?

With 16 years of diverse IT experience, I bring a unique blend of expertise of various roles such as Software Developer, DevOps Engineer, and now Cloud Solutions Architect. I am also a passionate Linux enthusiast with a knack for networking, hacking and tinkering with hardware. I thrive on solving complex challenges and embracing cutting-edge technologies. Beyond the keyboard, I’m a casual gamer and avid traveler, always exploring new horizons—both digital and physical.
